('c45ff9ca-6829-4d49-8f11-d2c3f31ebe15','Öl 10','BN 20|L 1317|B 1064',56.422,16.436,'[: eimunr : auk : kuna- … þeiʀ · -uku · kirþu · þisn · eftiʀ : kinu : fatran]','"Æimundr ok "Gunna[rr] … þæiʀ [k]umbl(?) gærðu þessa æftiʀ "Ginu(?) vitran.',NULL,'Eimundr and Gunnarr …, they made the monuments in memory of Gína(?) the sage.',NULL,'Williams (2004) ger inget förslag till tolkning av runföljden fatran.','Runsten','Sten','Öland'),
('bb37790e-43c4-46e4-a36a-cf895aaf6e71','Sm 71','L 1240',57.4658,14.7679,'× erinuorþr × let × reisa × stein × þena × eftiʀ × heka × faþur × sin × auk × heru × faþur : hans × auk × karl × hans × faþur … × heru × hans × faþur × auk × þiagn × hans × faþur × auk × eftiʀ × þe × lagfaþrga × fem ×','"Ærinvarðr let ræisa stæin þenna æftiʀ "Hægga, faður sinn, ok "Hæru, faður hans, ok "Karl, hans faður, [ok] "Hæru, hans faður, ok "Þiagn/"Þegn, hans faður, ok æftiʀ þa langfæðrga fæm.','Ärinvard lät resa denna sten efter Hägge, sin fader, och Hära, hans fader, och Karl, hans fader (och) Hära, hans fader, och Tägn, hans fader, och efter dessa fem förfäder.','Erinvarðr had this stone raised in memory of Heggi, his father and Hæra, his (i.e. Heggi''s) father, and Karl, his (i.e. Hæra''s) father and Hæra, his father and Þegn, his father and in memory of these five forefathers.',NULL,NULL,'Runsten','Diabas','Småland'),
