('aafad58b-f103-4c81-a56f-0211c1b42f80','Sö 56',NULL,58.9533,16.6689,'iak · uait : hastain : þa : hulmstain : bryþr · menr : rynasta : a : miþkarþi : setu : stain : auk : stafa : marga eftiʀ · fraystain · faþur · sin ·','Ek veit "Hástein þá "Holmstein brœðr menn rýnasta á "Miðgarði, settu stein ok stafa marga eptir "Freystein, fǫður sinn.','Jag vet bröderna Håsten och Holmsten vara de runkunnigaste män i världen. De satte sten och många stavar efter Frösten, sin fader.','I know Hásteinn and Holmsteinn, the most rune-skilled brothers in Middle Earth, placed many a stone and staff in memory of Freysteinn, their father.',NULL,NULL,'Jordfast block','Gnejs','Södermanland'),
