('6b22469a-4a2b-4fc9-84f1-0d8bc245abe2','Sm 132','L 1208|B 1035',57.7564,14.927,'(h)ilhi : raisti [:] s(t)(e)[i]n [:] (þ)eni : eftiʀ : fin : faþur · sin','"Hælgi ræisti stæin þenna æftiʀ "Finn, faður sinn.','Helge reste denna sten efter Finn, sin fader.','Helgi raised this stone in memory of Finnr, his father.',NULL,NULL,'Runsten','Röd granit','Småland'),
