('e04a7ec6-ac91-4271-b4f8-16f0ca78e663','G 35','L 1785',57.1335,18.3467,'×· katrin : ioans : husfyra : i sundru : han : lit : giara : þina : stain : yfir : moþur sina : botiauþu : iak[o]bs : kunu : sihlaihs:arf(a) : biþin : f(i)(r)(i) (h)enar : sial : bater : noster :×','"Katrin, "Iohans husfrøyia i "Sundru/"Sundre, hon let gæra þenna stæin yfiʀ moður sina "Botþiuðu, "Iakobs konu "Siglæiksarfa/"Sigsarve. Biðin fyriʀ hænnaʀ sial pater noster.','Katrin, Johans husfru i Sundre, hon lät göra denna sten över sin moder Botdjaud, hustru till Jakob, Siglaiks arvinge. Bedjen för hennes själ Pater noster.','Katrín, Jóhan in Sundr/Sundre''s housewife, she had this stone made over her mother Bótþjóð, wife of Jakobr of Sigleiksarfr/Sigleiksarfi. Pray Our Father for her soul.','Troligen senare hälften av 1200-talet',NULL,'Gravhäll','Röd kalksten','Gotland'),
('c52ca333-4720-45cc-8ddc-37e9ae9bfa8d','Sm 39',NULL,56.8649,14.161,'§A : kuni : sati : stin : þana : iftiʀ §B : suna : faþr : sin : milan : u… … mataʀ kuþa… :','§A "Gunni setti stein þenna eptir §B "Sona, fǫður sinn, mildan o[rða ok] matar góða[n].','§A Gunne satte denna sten efter §B Sune, sin fader, mild i ord och frikostig på mat.','§A Gunni placed this stone in memory of §B Soni, his father, gentle in speech and free with food.',NULL,NULL,'Runsten','Medelkornig gnejs','Småland'),
('d88b329a-fc06-40f4-b67b-2d429f1b2132','G 244','L 1728',57.6801,18.6319,'[+ iuan : iaka^ubs : arfi : huilis : hiar : af : norþa^rby : betar : ok : iakaupr : litu : gera : mik]','"Iohan, "Iakobs arfi, hvilis hiar af "Norðrby/"Norrbys. "Petar ok "Iakobr letu gæra mik.','Johan, Jakobs arvinge från Norrbys, vilar här. Petar och Jakob lät göra mig.','Jóhan of Norðrbýr/Norrbys, Jakobr''s heir, rests here. Pétr and Jakobr had me made.','1300-talet',NULL,'Gravhäll','Sten','Gotland'),
